Mn_ts3 drv[3] oe bus[3] 0 nmos_1v8 W=4u L=180n
Mp_ts3 drv[3] oeb bus[3] vdd pmos_1v8 W=8u L=180n
Rkeeper3 bus[3] 0 1meg
Ccbus3 bus[3] 0 50f
Mp_buf4 buf[4] din[4] vdd vdd pmos_1v8 W=4u L=180n
